= NPR on Kodi =
***this is still a work in progress.***

This addon will allow streaming of NPR news stations from NPR one.
as a part of the changes of the API you must sign up for a NPR ONE
presonal dev account(https://dev.npr.org/apply/). once done you can
create an application with will provide you with a app id and token.

you will need to update the addon configuration to include 

	
once this is done you can now log in and authorize your device for 
streaming with the provided code.